         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3172_0027"/>Herrn Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3172_0028"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Gruss aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb652">Prag</rs>!</hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Totalansicht von der <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb59763">Burg</rs> aus – 61.</hi></seg></seg></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3172_0028"/><date when="1902-03-29">29. 3. 1902</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Fröhliche Feiertage, <salute>mein lieber Freund,</salute> und viele
               Grüße! Es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chade, daß Du nicht hier bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t. Dein treuer <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></p><postscript><p><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb93">Hotel »Blauer Stern«</rs></hi><unclear>.</unclear></p></postscript></div>
      </body>
